com.hybris.cis.facade.subscription

Class SubscriptionServiceUserDetails

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hybris.cis.facade.subscription.SubscriptionServiceUserDetails
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails

    public class SubscriptionServiceUserDetails
extends Object
implements org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails

    Adapter for the subscription service's domain objects and Spring security.

    Provides for access to a user's subscribed services and also adds them to the list of granted authorities.
